//- layout.pug
doctype html
html(lang="fr")
    head
        meta(charset='UTF-8')
        meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
        link(rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.bunny.net")
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.bunny.net/css?family=figtree:400,500,600&display=swap")
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css")
        script(src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com")
        block title
            title GestionPro - Le logiciel de gestion de budget

    body(class="bg-white border-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-900")
        nav(class="dark:bg-gray-800")
            div(class="max-w-screen-xl flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between mx-auto p-4")
                //- Logo et titre
                a(href="/" class="flex items-center pb-4 border-b border-b-gray-800") 
                    h2(class="font-bold text-2xl text-white") Gestion
                        span(class="text-white px-2 rounded-md bg-blue-700") Pro
                //- Menu de navigation
                div(class="hidden w-full md:block md:w-auto dark:bg-gray-800" id="navbar-default")
                    ul(class="font-medium flex flex-col p-4 md:p-0 mt-4 border border-gray-100 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 md:flex-row md:space-x-8 rtl:space-x-reverse md:mt-0 md:border-0 md:bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 md:dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-800")
                        li: a(href="/" class="block py-2 px-3 text-gray-900 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 md:hover:bg-transparent md:border-0 md:hover:text-blue-700 md:p-0 dark:text-white md:dark:hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-white md:dark:hover:bg-transparent" aria-current="page") Accueil
                        li: a(href="/about" class="block py-2 px-3 text-gray-900 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 md:hover:bg-transparent md:border-0 md:hover:text-blue-700 md:p-0 dark:text-white md:dark:hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-white md:dark:hover:bg-transparent") À propos
                        li: a(href="/contact" class="block py-2 px-3 text-gray-900 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 md:hover:bg-transparent md:border-0 md:hover:text-blue-700 md:p-0 dark:text-white md:dark:hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-white md:dark:hover:bg-transparent") Contact
                        li: a(href="login" class="block py-2 px-3 text-gray-900 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 md:hover:bg-transparent md:border-0 md:hover:text-blue-700 md:p-0 dark:text-white md:dark:hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-white md:dark:hover:bg-transparent") Connexion 
        block content
            section(class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900")
                div(class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-16 mx-auto text-center lg:py-32 lg:px-6")
                    h1(class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white")
                        | Simplifiez votre gestion financière avec 
                        span(class="text-blue-700") GestionPro
                    p(class="mt-6 text-lg font-normal text-gray-500 lg:text-xl sm:px-16 xl:px-48 dark:text-gray-400")
                        | Gérez vos budgets personnels et professionnels avec un outil puissant, facile à utiliser et entièrement sécurisé.
                    div(class="mt-8 flex justify-center space-x-4")
                        a(href="/signup" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-white bg-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 dark:focus:ring-blue-900")
                            | Essayez gratuitement
                        a(href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-gray-900 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-100 dark:text-white dark:border-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-800")
                            | En savoir plus

            section(class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-16")
                div(class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto text-center")
                    h2(class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6") Pourquoi choisir GestionPro ?
                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8")
                        div(class="flex flex-col items-center text-center")
                            i(class="bx bx-wallet text-6xl text-blue-700 mb-4")
                            h3(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") Gestion de budget simplifiée
                            p(class="mt-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") Planifiez, suivez et optimisez vos budgets vacances en quelques clics.
                        div(class="flex flex-col items-center text-center")
                            i(class="ri-secure-payment-line text-6xl text-blue-700 mb-4")
                            h3(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") Sécurité maximale
                            p(class="mt-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") Vos données sont protégées grâce à un chiffrement de bout en bout.
                        div(class="flex flex-col items-center text-center")
                            i(class="ri-team-line text-6xl text-blue-700 mb-4")
                            h3(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") Collaboration facile
                            p(class="mt-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") Enregistrez vos dépenses facilement entre amis.

            section(class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 py-16")
                div(class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto text-center")
                    h2(class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6") Ce que disent nos utilisateurs
                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8")
                        div(class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-800")
                            p(class="text-lg italic text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") "GestionPro a transformé la façon dont je gère mes finances avec mes amis. Un outil indispensable !"
                            span(class="block mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") - Marie Dupont
                        div(class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-800")
                            p(class="text-lg italic text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") "Simple, rapide et fiable. Je ne pourrais plus m'en passer !"
                            span(class="block mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") - Jean Martin
                        div(class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-800")
                            p(class="text-lg italic text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400") "Une solution intuitive pour gérer des budgets vacances entre amis."
                            span(class="block mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white") - Sophie Lambert

            section(class="bg-blue-700 text-white py-16")
                div(class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto text-center")
                    h2(class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6") Prêt à commencer ?
                    p(class="text-lg font-normal mb-8") Rejoignez des milliers d'utilisateurs qui ont adopté GestionPro pour simplifier leur gestion financière.
                    div(class="flex justify-center space-x-4")
                        a(href="/signup" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-medium text-center text-blue-700 bg-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-300")
                            | Commencez maintenant
                        a(href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-medium text-center border border-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-900")
                            | Contactez-nous


        footer(class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow m-4 dark:bg-gray-800")
            div(class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-4 md:py-8")
                div(class="m:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between")
                    a(href="#" class="flex items-center pb-4 border-b border-b-gray-800") 
                    h2(class="font-bold text-2xl text-white") Gestion
                        span(class="text-white px-2 rounded-md bg-blue-700") Pro
                    ul(class="flex flex-wrap items-center mb-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 sm:mb-0 dark:text-gray-400")
                        li
                            a(href="/about" class="hover:underline me-4 md:me-6") À propos
                        li
                            a(href="#" class="hover:underline me-4 md:me-6") Politique de confidentialité
                        li  
                            a(href="#" class="hover:underline me-4 md:me-6") Licence
                        li 
                            a(href="/contact" class="hover:underline") Contact
                hr(class="my-6 border-gray-200 sm:mx-auto dark:border-gray-700 lg:my-8")
                span(class="block text-sm text-gray-500 sm:text-center dark:text-gray-400") © 2024 
                    a(href="/" class="hover:underline") GestionPro. Tous droits réservés.

    

